handbrake (1.6.1-1) bookworm; urgency=low
  * CORE
   - Fixed a potential decoder issue that could cause desync with audio
   
  * LINUX
   - Fixed translations missing updates as part of 1.6.0
   - Bulgarian (Български)
   - Corsican (Corsu)
   - Dutch (Nederlands)
   - German (Deutsch)
   - Spanish (Español)
   - Fixed (partially) Intel QSV hardware detection
   - Fixed a potential crash when canceling an Intel QSV encode
   - Fixed building with -Werror=format-security by adding missing format strings where needed
   
  * CLI
   - Fixed inability to name external subtitles tracks using --subname

